__bs__ Perhaps there are other states that we can &apos;t access because of how our minds are structured but other minds possibly could access them .
__bs__ Now , let me be clear about what I &apos;m not saying . I &apos;m not saying that science is guaranteed to map this space , or that we will have scientific answers to every conceivable moral question .
